<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-24 18:53 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> 'What Lies Beneath' Tops Box Office  </HEADLINE>
By TOM HARRIGAN
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES (AP) -- A summer of film debuts burying their
opposition continued with ''What Lies Beneath,'' a ghostly tale
starring Michelle Pfeiffer and Harrison Ford, which earned $29.7
million in its first three days.
</P>
